           </ul>
          </div>
          <span style="text-align: center; display: block;">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">
               Sign your bnb up now
              </a>
          </span>
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
          <div>
            <h2>
              Booking a bnb online?
