              <li>View all your bookings</li>
              <li>Search BnB's easily and effectively</li>
              <li>Hassle free, time saving and clutter free</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <span style="text-align: center; display: block;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">
            Sign up now to start booking!
            </a>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
